<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_9e460fc3-6d17-43f0-a182-9a79d3c97485" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>B6O1</sptc><title id="_766eec10-064f-46f4-85cf-68b9138d4386">Objective</title><archive-num>2019: BO6</archive-num><subclause id="_289a93cf-84dd-45d1-8f86-017cc2388c1b" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_c23905d5-f73b-4fa8-bca3-9bed8a64e27e">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The Objective of this Part is to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_59c2857b-24fd-4476-bbd9-229ed5d50db7">safeguard people from illness, injury or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1362_2.0.0.xml#_ba5bd5ee-ef5f-41be-b153-43835028cd86" id="_87f3cdee-b9be-4680-a276-3aaa442f3bce" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">loss</xref> (including <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1362_2.0.0.xml#_ba5bd5ee-ef5f-41be-b153-43835028cd86" id="_4912f8fd-bae8-425c-9c06-02a1a9da326f" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">loss</xref> of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1186_0.6.0.xml#_905252bf-2ff1-43f8-ae81-2949aa116fee" id="_9799e689-db2e-4c73-a06d-2a6cfbbcf538" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">amenity</xref>) due to the failure of a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1422_4.4.0.xml#_bd764954-3054-4109-81f2-164feefc5058" id="_b391935d-d043-49fc-a982-17581dd4c663" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">rainwater service</xref>; and</li><li id="_8865b95a-b089-4741-b857-e8254847f15b">conserve water; and</li><li id="_0fc148b0-cbaf-4df9-a93c-efebd2324e17">safeguard the environment; and</li><li id="_6913dbb0-84d9-4267-9d10-b1dd00876ef2">safeguard public and private infrastructure; and</li><li id="_0f553ce0-3f0b-4bc7-b8ab-bc35f270be2a">ensure that a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publi